CHANGE LOG/RELEASE NOTES
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
NEWEST CHANGES FOR THE NOTES EDITION:
(* indicates a big/important change)

--------
1.01   |
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    1. Added the 'Soc' operator (\soc) for the socle of a module.
    2. Changed '\mpar{}' definition to include \raggedright formatting.
    3. Added the 'Res' operator (\res) for the residue of a function.
   *4. Stopped loading the 'imakeidx' package. Now loading 'makeidx' package.
        At one point, the 'mathtools' package was incompatible with 'expl3'.
        This may still be the case. I believe that 'imakeidx' is also
        incompatible. At any rate, loading both packages simultaneously causes
        a big error with 'expl3', so we will use 'makeidx' in place of
        'imakeidx'.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

